Source: NZ Farmer
Author:
Vol / Page: 1238
Edition:
Quote: I would strongly advise making use of them [pets] as indicated as decoys. Thus when moving sheep, if the owner of the pet goes ahead with the decoy, it will be found there is little if any use for dogs or strong language.
